类 Pokemon

  • java.lang.Object
    • Pokemon
  • public class Pokemon
extends java.lang.Object
    This class intends to contain all attributes of a pokemon which could be the value object being stored in the hashtable.
    版本:
    1.0
    作者:
    Tianwei Bao, Seungjun Chong, Minghao Zhou, Liangqi Cai, Zhiwei Cao, Jiahe Jin, Yunzhao Liu

    • 构造器详细资料

      • Pokemon

        public Pokemon​(java.lang.String name,
               java.lang.String type1,
               java.lang.String type2,
               int hp,
               int attack,
               int defense,
               int spAttack,
               int spDefense,
               int speed,
               int total,
               boolean legendary,
               boolean favorite)
        The non-default constructor is used to set the one specific pokemon in this class.
        参数:
        attack - the int value of Attack the pokemon possesses
        defense - the int value of Defense the pokemon possesses
        hp - the int value of HP the pokemon possesses
        legendary - the boolean state of Legendary character the pokemon is
        name - the String name of the pokemon is
        spAttack - the int value of Special Attack the pokemon possesses
        spDefense - the int value of Special Defense the pokemon possesses
        speed - the int value of Speed the pokemon possesses
        total - the int value of Total Values the pokemon has by adding all other values
        type1 - the String First Type of the pokemon has
        type2 - the String Second Type of the pokemon has
        favorite - the favorite state of the pokemon is
